
Prerequisites for EasyOCaml are the same like for OCaml (see INSTALL)

Steps:

 $ ./configure [-prefix <path/to/install/dir>]
 $ ./build/smallworld.sh
 $ ./build/install.sh
and optional
 $ ./boot/ocamlrun boot/myocamlbuild easyadd/htmlErrorReport.cmo easyadd/structuredErrorReport.cmo
to use HTML output suitable for easyadd/htmlreport/easyocaml.js or structured output for some future OCaml IDE
 $ ocaml/c -easy -easyerrorreport _build/easyadd/htmlErrorReport.cmo # or _build/easyadd/structuredErrorReport.cmo
